				</li><li class="footnote " id="footnote28-09691_002_035"><a name="-09691_002_035"> </a>
					<span class="label"><a name="footnote28-09691_002_035">28.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/84.38?lang=spa#37" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 84:38</a>.</p>
