					<span class="label"><a name="footnote34-09691_002_035">34.</a></span>
					<p class="">Véase <a href="https://www.lds.org/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/20.37?lang=spa#36" target="_blank">Doctrina y Convenios 20:37</a>.</p>
